        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;max-width:600px;padding:20px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;\">    <h2 style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:500;\">Thank you for your application</h2>    <p>Hi {{ $json.Name }},</p>    <p>Thank you for taking the time to apply for the <strong>Software Developer</strong> position and for sharing your CV and cover letter with us. We genuinely appreciate your interest.</p>    <div style=\"background:#fafafa;border-left:4px solid #d1d5db;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin:20px 0;\">     <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;\">After careful consideration of all applications, we won't be moving forward with your application at this time. This was a competitive process and the decision was not easy.</p>   </div>    <p>We encourage you to keep building your skills and experience — the tech industry moves fast and we'd love to see you apply again in the future as you grow.</p>    <p>We wish you all the best in your job search and future career.</p>    <p>Warm regards,<br>   <strong>The Hiring Team</strong></p>    <hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #eee;margin:24px 0;\">   <p style=\"font-size:11px;color:#bbb;\">This email was sent automatically via our recruitment pipeline.</p>  </div>",
